            <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1149"
              hreflang="en">IETF RFC 1149</a> del 1990-04-01:
              <em>A Standard for the Transmission of IP Datagrams
              on Avian Carriers</em>) [<a href=
              "rfc1149.htm">local file rfc1149</a>]
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Dicembre 1974: prima specifica di <em>TCP</em>
        (Transfer Control Protocol) per internetworking
        </li>
